{
  "video_id": "rSMO4pHe3HE",
  "title": "Inside Game of Thrones: A Story in Score (HBO)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1300.0,
      "end_time": 3602.0,
      "text": "♪ (GAME OF THRONES THEME SONG PLAYS ON GUITAR) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16470.0,
      "end_time": 17148.0,
      "text": "My name&#39;s Ramin Djawadi,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17583.0,
      "end_time": 19151.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re in my studio  in Santa Monica"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19252.0,
      "end_time": 21287.0,
      "text": "where I write all the music for Game of Thrones."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21454.0,
      "end_time": 24890.0,
      "text": "♪ (THEME SONG CONTINUES) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25524.0,
      "end_time": 28661.0,
      "text": "I started out on the organ  when I was four years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28761.0,
      "end_time": 31130.0,
      "text": "and then when I was 13, I picked up the guitar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31230.0,
      "end_time": 33650.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s when I really got serious about music"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33165.0,
      "end_time": 34466.0,
      "text": "and started practicing a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34567.0,
      "end_time": 36602.0,
      "text": "And it was the movie The Magnificent Seven..."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36702.0,
      "end_time": 39138.0,
      "text": "Elmer Bernstein&#39;s score  triggered something in me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39238.0,
      "end_time": 41272.0,
      "text": "and the recognizable themes that you could hum"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41373.0,
      "end_time": 42675.0,
      "text": "when you turned off the film."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43750.0,
      "end_time": 44577.0,
      "text": "♪ (GAME OF THRONES THEME PLAYS) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44677.0,
      "end_time": 47247.0,
      "text": "I knew that that&#39;s what I wanted to be, a film composer."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49282.0,
      "end_time": 51383.0,
      "text": "The beauty about  music in film is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51484.0,
      "end_time": 53152.0,
      "text": "without any dialogue on the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53252.0,
      "end_time": 55188.0,
      "text": "you are able to guide the audience."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55288.0,
      "end_time": 56321.0,
      "text": "And with Game of Thrones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56689.0,
      "end_time": 57924.0,
      "text": "we are able  to guide the audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 58691.0,
      "end_time": 60159.0,
      "text": "either in the right direction  or the wrong direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 60259.0,
      "end_time": 61661.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s something  that&#39;s been fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 62561.0,
      "end_time": 65230.0,
      "text": "By moods or by playing a certain theme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 65331.0,
      "end_time": 66966.0,
      "text": "you are able to tell a story."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 68000.0,
      "end_time": 71704.0,
      "text": "♪ (GAME OF THRONES THEME CONTINUES ON GUITAR) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 74741.0,
      "end_time": 76742.0,
      "text": "The biggest challenge was just finding the right tone"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76843.0,
      "end_time": 79110.0,
      "text": "for the show, that when you hear the score,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79111.0,
      "end_time": 81147.0,
      "text": "that you know this is  Game of Thrones."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83349.0,
      "end_time": 85385.0,
      "text": "From the beginning,  we knew we wanted themes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85485.0,
      "end_time": 87886.0,
      "text": "but we also knew that we couldn&#39;t have too many themes"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87986.0,
      "end_time": 90489.0,
      "text": "right away, because there&#39;s obviously a lot of characters."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90589.0,
      "end_time": 91890.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a lot of  different houses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91990.0,
      "end_time": 92926.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot of plots."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93493.0,
      "end_time": 95270.0,
      "text": "And if you convolute it  too soon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95495.0,
      "end_time": 97196.0,
      "text": "I think it actually would have been confusing for the audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97930.0,
      "end_time": 101200.0,
      "text": "so we actually, on purpose,  held off with themes  for certain characters."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101300.0,
      "end_time": 103869.0,
      "text": "For example, Theon, or the Greyjoy theme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103969.0,
      "end_time": 105637.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t exist until season two."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 108407.0,
      "end_time": 110442.0,
      "text": "Arya, for example, we used the Stark theme for her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110543.0,
      "end_time": 111878.0,
      "text": "but she also has her own theme"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 111978.0,
      "end_time": 113246.0,
      "text": "once she got on her own."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128561.0,
      "end_time": 129762.0,
      "text": "In Game of Thrones, we always laugh"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 130294.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131697.0,
      "text": "because every season, we sit down and we say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 131797.0,
      "end_time": 134501.0,
      "text": "\"Okay, which instrument  haven&#39;t we used yet?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135568.0,
      "end_time": 136735.0,
      "text": "(HORN BLOWING)"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136836.0,
      "end_time": 138571.0,
      "text": "Most of the orchestral instruments I&#39;ve used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 138671.0,
      "end_time": 141673.0,
      "text": "so strings, french horns, trombones, percussion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 141774.0,
      "end_time": 143876.0,
      "text": "the didgeridoo we&#39;ve used  for the Wildlings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 143976.0,
      "end_time": 146513.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s kind of an interesting instrument that&#39;s different."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148781.0,
      "end_time": 150917.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s an Armenian duduk  that we used"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151170.0,
      "end_time": 152510.0,
      "text": "for the Dothrakis."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 152719.0,
      "end_time": 154888.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like an ethnic version  of an oboe basically."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156556.0,
      "end_time": 157923.0,
      "text": "When I start working on a scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158257.0,
      "end_time": 160159.0,
      "text": "I just watch the scene without even playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 160259.0,
      "end_time": 161660.0,
      "text": "I try to hear the tempo  in my head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 161760.0,
      "end_time": 164300.0,
      "text": "and once I have that, I can play along."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 164864.0,
      "end_time": 167333.0,
      "text": "I now proclaim Cersei of the House Lannister"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167433.0,
      "end_time": 169668.0,
      "text": "protector of the Seven Kingdoms."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 169768.0,
      "end_time": 171170.0,
      "text": "♪ (VIOLINS PLAY) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 171938.0,
      "end_time": 173405.0,
      "text": "RAMIN DJAWADI:  I usually start writing  on one instrument first."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 173506.0,
      "end_time": 175107.0,
      "text": "It can be piano,  it can be string pad."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 175207.0,
      "end_time": 176341.0,
      "text": "I sketch out the scene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176709.0,
      "end_time": 178244.0,
      "text": "and then once I feel I have the right shape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178978.0,
      "end_time": 180779.0,
      "text": "then I go back and then I start arranging and orchestrating the scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180880.0,
      "end_time": 183248.0,
      "text": "And then I add  all the different layers  of instrumentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 183349.0,
      "end_time": 186685.0,
      "text": "♪ (ORCHESTRAL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 186785.0,
      "end_time": 188721.0,
      "text": "While the episode  is still edited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 188821.0,
      "end_time": 190322.0,
      "text": "everything just stays  in the computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 190422.0,
      "end_time": 191523.0,
      "text": "and everything&#39;s  just done digitally."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191624.0,
      "end_time": 193250.0,
      "text": "And once the picture is locked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 193125.0,
      "end_time": 194930.0,
      "text": "then I go in  and actually record it"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 194193.0,
      "end_time": 195228.0,
      "text": "with real musicians."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 195628.0,
      "end_time": 197495.0,
      "text": "And I feel that&#39;s the most rewarding thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 197596.0,
      "end_time": 200466.0,
      "text": "I still get goosebumps when I hear them play the music."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 201733.0,
      "end_time": 204169.0,
      "text": "I just get huge inspiration  from just seeing the sets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 204270.0,
      "end_time": 205971.0,
      "text": "from just seeing  how epic everything is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 206710.0,
      "end_time": 207206.0,
      "text": "and then meeting the actors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 207306.0,
      "end_time": 208507.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s inspirational for me as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 208941.0,
      "end_time": 210476.0,
      "text": "Just standing on the side  and just watching."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 211100.0,
      "end_time": 213780.0,
      "text": "I wanna just go back to the studio right away and start writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 213179.0,
      "end_time": 215848.0,
      "text": "♪ (PIANO PLAYING) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 216382.0,
      "end_time": 219185.0,
      "text": "DJAWADI: This is the piece  from episode 6-10."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 219285.0,
      "end_time": 221587.0,
      "text": "This long build up  of Cersei&#39;s trial."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 221688.0,
      "end_time": 223255.0,
      "text": "The interesting thing about this piece is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 223822.0,
      "end_time": 225791.0,
      "text": "this is actually the first time in Game of Thrones history"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 225891.0,
      "end_time": 228394.0,
      "text": "that we used the piano. So the minute that plays..."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 228494.0,
      "end_time": 230363.0,
      "text": "♪ (PIANO PLAYING) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 231731.0,
      "end_time": 233966.0,
      "text": "DJAWADI:  The audience immediately  is alerted, and they&#39;ll go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 234660.0,
      "end_time": 236702.0,
      "text": "\"Wait, we have never heard  this instrument before this."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 236902.0,
      "end_time": 237970.0,
      "text": "Something is not right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 238604.0,
      "end_time": 240739.0,
      "text": "-So the piece plays on... -♪ (PIANO CONTINUES) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 241173.0,
      "end_time": 244243.0,
      "text": "It starts off very minimal, and it slowly builds over..."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 244344.0,
      "end_time": 246120.0,
      "text": "I think the piece is six and a half minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 246112.0,
      "end_time": 247146.0,
      "text": "seven minutes long."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 247713.0,
      "end_time": 251751.0,
      "text": "The next element that comes in are two boys singing."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 251851.0,
      "end_time": 255355.0,
      "text": "♪ (CHOIR BOYS SINGING) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 257790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259425.00000000003,
      "text": "When you see the kids  with the knife in the hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 259524.0,
      "end_time": 261920.0,
      "text": "and then Pycelle gets stabbed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 261192.0,
      "end_time": 262460.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s when it switches to the organ,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 262561.0,
      "end_time": 264960.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s when the choir comes in."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 265231.0,
      "end_time": 267400.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s really the next  step up of when you realize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 267500.0,
      "end_time": 269435.0,
      "text": "\"Wow, this is all going  wrong right now.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 269802.0,
      "end_time": 271871.0,
      "text": "And now the piece is really starting to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 271971.0,
      "end_time": 274807.0,
      "text": "More instruments come in,  and the organ gets busier."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 274907.0,
      "end_time": 277800.0,
      "text": "And then the orchestra actually  doesn&#39;t come in"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 277109.0,
      "end_time": 278176.0,
      "text": "until the very end."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 278277.0,
      "end_time": 280380.0,
      "text": "♪ (ORCHESTRAL MUSIC PLAYING) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 284349.0,
      "end_time": 285584.0,
      "text": "This section&#39;s  actually interesting"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 286180.0,
      "end_time": 288219.0,
      "text": "because I actually snuck in  the main title theme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 288321.0,
      "end_time": 289488.0,
      "text": "so you can hear it right here."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 289588.0,
      "end_time": 294527.0,
      "text": "♪ (THEME SONG PLAYS) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 297596.0,
      "end_time": 300899.0,
      "text": "Every year I go, \"Okay, now I really have to do something that I haven&#39;t done before.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 300999.0,
      "end_time": 303803.0,
      "text": "The show definitely  takes it up another notch  every season."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 303903.0,
      "end_time": 305537.0,
      "text": "Even though whenever I think it&#39;s not possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 305637.0,
      "end_time": 307740.0,
      "text": "they still are able to elevate it yet another notch."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 307840.0,
      "end_time": 309508.0,
      "text": "And so I gotta do the same with the music."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 309608.0,
      "end_time": 313790.0,
      "text": "♪ (ORCHESTRAL MUSIC INTENSIFIES) ♪"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 314947.0,
      "end_time": 317517.0,
      "text": "-(EXPLOSIVE BLAST) -♪ (MUSIC STOPS) ♪"
    }
  ]
}